492
00:23:23,833 --> 00:23:25,166
[Motoko]
I love Yuki.

493
00:23:25,250 --> 00:23:26,916
I love his
beautiful silver hair

494
00:23:27,000 --> 00:23:28,916
and the way it
sparkles in the sunlight,

495
00:23:29,000 --> 00:23:31,416
the way his luscious
lashes caress his cheeks

496
00:23:31,500 --> 00:23:32,916
when his eyes
are closed,

497
00:23:33,000 --> 00:23:35,083
his sweet,
sweet voice.

498
00:23:35,166 --> 00:23:38,833
I love everything.
Yuki is my everything.

499
00:23:38,916 --> 00:23:40,333
Aaaah, Yuki!

500
00:23:40,416 --> 00:23:42,541
It is my fate to be
forever cursed and blessed

501
00:23:42,625 --> 00:23:44,458
by visions of
your angelic face.

502
00:23:44,541 --> 00:23:47,083
Like a prick upon the
thorn of a rose, your love--

503
00:23:47,166 --> 00:23:49,833
For the love of--
Keep it down Motoko!

504
00:23:49,916 --> 00:23:51,291
You're waking
the neighbors!

505
00:23:51,375 --> 00:23:53,541
Mother! Haven't you
ever heard of knocking?

506
00:23:53,625 --> 00:23:54,875
Sure! "Knock,
knock, knock!

507
00:23:54,958 --> 00:23:56,750
Can I come in
Princess Loudmouth?"

508
00:23:56,833 --> 00:23:57,916
It wouldn't
be like this

509
00:23:58,000 --> 00:23:59,541
if I hadn't been born
a year too early!

510
00:23:59,625 --> 00:24:01,750
What in the world are
you babbling about now?

